    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty in person! It is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and making sure it stayed spotless. It drives like an absolute dream! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Come swing by and take a look, I promise you\u2019re going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
