    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering, featuring the legendary S54 inline-six engine with independent throttle bodies and Double VANOS timing, all maintained to factory tolerances. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement, ensuring optimal torsional rigidity. Power is managed via a precise Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip M-Variable differential. Every mechanical component, from the high-revving valvetrain to the suspension bushings, exhibits zero fatigue, offering a true-to-spec driving experience. This is a collector-grade example with a pristine undercarriage and a drivetrain that has never seen track-day heat cycling.",
